      <title>Citadel 允许客户获利了结，但大多数客户拒绝了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/citadel-offered-to-let-clients-redeem-profits-but-had-few-takers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，Citadel 的旗舰策略取得了约 15% 的收益，该公司邀请客户套现利润，但绝大多数客户选择将资金留在该多策略对冲基金中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/citadel-offered-to-let-clients-redeem-profits-but-had-few-takers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 18:54:10 GMT</pubDate>
